Bottomless margaritas with tacos for only £35 🤯

If you’re looking for fun places to go in London or your next date night idea, make sure to check out The Palm House in Victoria. 

This offer is available every Friday from 12pm and they even have a DJ to keep you up dancing all night 🎧 We’ve got eyes bigger than our stomachs so we also tucked into some delicious side dishes 🤩
